# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  EmailJS Configuration — Contact Form
#  
#  HOW TO USE:
#  1. Copy this file and rename it to .env  (never commit .env)
#       cp .env.example .env
#  2. Fill in your real values from https://www.emailjs.com
#  3. Run: npm install && npm start
#
#  WHERE TO GET THESE VALUES:
#    SERVICE_ID   → EmailJS Dashboard → Email Services → your service
#    TEMPLATE_ID  → EmailJS Dashboard → Email Templates → your template
#    PUBLIC_KEY   → EmailJS Dashboard → Account → General → Public Key
#
#  IMPORTANT:
#    - Create React App REQUIRES the REACT_APP_ prefix for env vars
#    - Never rename the prefix to VITE_ — that is for Vite projects only
#    - Never commit the real .env file — it is already in .gitignore
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

REACT_APP_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=your_service_id_here
REACT_APP_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID=your_template_id_here
REACT_APP_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=your_public_key_here
